Summer Drinks Ep 10 : Saunf Ka Sharbat🍀

This is a traditional method of hydrating body at the time of scorching heat. It helps in keeping our body cool and hydrated at the time of heat strokes.

Ingredients:
1/2 cup Saunf/fennel☘️
1/2 cup Mishri🥡
8/10 black peppercorns🖤
2/3 green Cardamon/ elaichi🍃
Ice cubes🧊
Black salt🧂
Basil seeds🌿
Chilled water💧💧 

Mix well & enjoy 🍀🍸
